{
  "texts": [
    "Transformers have since proven to be not only valuable for NLP but also in other areas, such as computer vision (Dosovitskiy et al., 2020; Khan et al., 2022) because they can accept different modalities of input as tokens (Xu et al., 2023).",
    "For our argument, we must examine whether transformers demonstrate promise along the dimensions we have stated before.",
    "If they do so, it will mean that transformers could be further exploited for better xAI techniques in healthcare.",
    "In this section, we thus review the recent literature surrounding the performance of transformers at social and abductive reasoning.",
    "While some of these studies are preliminary, they give us the most up-to-date picture of AI's abilities."
  ]
}